kubejs.ponder.fluid_tank.text_1: Right-click with empty hand + shift on the Fluid Tank (not Fake Fluid Tank)
kubejs.ponder.fluid_tank.text_2: Place Depot in these areas with red particle effects
kubejs.ponder.fluid_tank.text_3: Right-click on the corresponding item and place it on the Depot
kubejs.ponder.fluid_tank.text_4: Then pour the corresponding fluid into the middle Fluid Tank(Right click on the bucket directly for survival mode, only this integration package can be implemented~)
kubejs.ponder.fluid_tank.text_5: Finally, hold the corresponding item and Right-click on the Fluid Tank
kubejs.ponder.fluid_tank.text_6: After starting the crafting, particle effects will appear. Wait for the particle effects to finish before the crafting is complete
kubejs.ponder.mana_pool.text_1: Right-click with empty hand + shift on the Mana Pool (not Fake Mana Pool)
kubejs.ponder.mana_pool.text_2: Place Element Containers in these areas with red particle effects
kubejs.ponder.mana_pool.text_3: Place Source Jars in these areas with green particle effects
kubejs.ponder.mana_pool.text_4: A certain amount of four Elements are required in the Element Container (the positions of the four Elements can be freely selected)
kubejs.ponder.mana_pool.text_5: A certain amount of Source is required in the Source Jar (all 4 Source Jars require it)
kubejs.ponder.mana_pool.text_6: The middle mana pool also requires a certain amount of mana
kubejs.ponder.mana_pool.text_7: Finally, hold the corresponding item and Right-click on the mana pool (not shift + Right-click)
kubejs.ponder.mana_pool.text_8: After starting the crafting, particle effects will appear. Wait for the particle effects to finish before the crafting is complete
kubejs.ponder.dream_portal_core.text_1: This mana pool can be easily replaced (with'#cwe:mana_pool')
kubejs.ponder.dream_portal_core.text_2: This machine must open the door in order to work. Hold the Wand Of Forset in hand. In each Mana Pool, if there is 10000 mana, Right-click on the Dream Portal Core can be activated
kubejs.ponder.dream_portal_core.text_3: This machine consumes each Mana Pools of 1000 mana each time it works
kubejs.ponder.dream_portal_core.text_4: This machine has Facing, please refer to the structure in CM for specific structure. (If you don't know how to view it, please refer to the prompt in the ftbquest.)
